'''''The New Jedi Order: Knightfall II: Jedi Fire''''' was the second book in the canceled [[Knightfall Trilogy]] of the [[Star Wars: The New Jedi Order|New Jedi Order]] series. It was to be written by [[Michael Jan Friedman]], with the cover art by [[Terese Nielsen]]. The plot would have dealt with [[Danni Quee]] and [[Jorallen]] seeking to stop the [[Yuuzhan Vong]] from murdering the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]].

